          <p class='first-para'>
            moved Amendment No. 55:
            <q>Page 14, line 15, at end insert "and every effort has been made to inform each parent or guardian or other persons holding parental responsibility</q>
            The noble Baroness said: I rise to move this amendment, the meaning of which is self-evident, conscious of the fact that the Minister made some reference to this matter in reply to an earlier group of
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_154gc' title='Col. 154GC &mdash; HL Deb 02 July 2002 vol 637 c154GC' name='column_154gc' href='#column_154gc' rel='bookmark'>154GC</a>
